info.name: /trdelete
info.description: Delete all the temporary channels in your server, and move the members to a new channel, if you want.
examples: /trdelete - Delete all the temporary channels created in your server.
/trdelete 929774135620550736 - Delete all the temporary channels and move all the users to the channel of ID `929774135620550736`.
/trdelete #Party - Delete all the temporary channels and move all the users to the channel `Party`.
